        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of a first-ever left hemisphere ischemic or hemorrhagic stroke at least 6
             months prior to entry into the study;

          -  minimum ability for shoulder humeral elevation;

          -  upper-extremity motor function Fugl-Meyer (FM) score â‰¥ 15(out of 66);

          -  absence of neurological or muscular disorders that interfere with neuromuscular
             function;

